text.tspan: Let us seek first the kingdom of God
Daily pursue the growth in life
As one new man full grown in Christ,
Pay the price, extra portion buy,
A full-grown bride Christ’s longing satisfies.
Oh, what joy! What deep delight!
Both God and man are satisfied!
“Come, freely drink!” say the Spirit and the bride.
We’ll be the overcomers God desires!
Drink! Overflow! Living waters, men supply!
